<section data-bs-spy="scroll" data-bs-target="#navbar-example2" data-bs-root-margin="0px 0px -40%" data-bs-smooth-scroll="false" class="scrollspy-example" tabindex="0">
    <div id="master1" class="overview">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <h3 class="heading">Data Science, Machine Learning and Edge AI <span>Course Overview</span></h3>
            <div class="row gy-4">
                <div class="col-lg-7">
                    <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                          <div class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                Introduction To Data Science Machine Learning And Edge AI Course 
                            </button>
                          </div>
                          <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>Data Science, Machine Learning, and Edge AI are the emerging technologies of modern times. These technologies are developed to help businesses extract actionable information from a set of raw data. Organizations are recruiting those professionals who have expertise in collecting large amounts of unstructured data with the help of Machine Learning, Data Science and Edge AI on an advanced level.</p>
                                <p>Owing to the increasing demand for data science and machine learning professionals, it is important for you to pursue an online data science course. You can enroll in Online Certification in Applied Data Science, Machine Learning and Edge AI By E&ICT Academy, IIT Guwahati. This course is designed to teach you scientific methods, locate and understand big data patterns.</p>
                                <p>This 6 months Advanced Certification in Online Data Science, Machine Learning, and Edge AI by E&ICT Academy, IIT Guwahati is designed to not only provide a hands-on practical approach but also includes various use cases so that students can explore practical industrial requirements and work culture.</p>
                                <p>The IoT Academy is leading the position to provide the best <strong>data science and machine learning</strong> training programs. The program is designed to make candidates understand the following:</p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Introduction to Edge AI, Machine Learning, Data Science, Deep Learning, etc.</li>
                                    <li>Real-time examples where Machine Learning & Artificial Intelligence can be used to solve real-world business problems.</li>
                                    <li>Introduction to Natural Language Processing, Supervised Learning, and Unsupervised Learning and more.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                          <div class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                How Can This Program Help You? 
                            </button>
                          </div>
                          <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p class="fw-bold">Enhancing Your Skill Set</p>
                                <p>With a well-designed advanced certificate program, you can enhance your skill set by learning complex things in a much easier way with changing dynamics of emerging technologies. </p>
